blogs.title: Let's do this!
blogs.description:
Hello! I'm Alex!

This is a blog for recording my weight loss journey and also writing about health and nutrition.

I've been trying for over a year, casually, to lose weight but this year I am putting myself in high gear and I'm going to be working as hard as I can to get into shape! This isn't just about weight loss for me though, I have found that exercise and healthy eating help keep my anxiety and depression in check. So this is also a whole lifestyle change that I am trying to stick to.

I also just started a nutrition course and I'm hoping to start an online health food company with my mom!

 Starting weight: 220lbs

Goal weight #1: 210lbs

Ultimate goal weight: 160lbs?
